  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Magic action, you can magically alter the weight of one object or creature you can see within 30 feet of you. The object or creature must be Large or smaller. The target's weight is halved or doubled for up to 1 minute or until you use this feature again. You can end this effect at any time with no action required.<br /><br /><strong>Increase Density</strong>. While the weight of a creature is halved by this effect, the creature's Speed increases by 10 feet, it can jump twice as far as normal, it has Disadvantage on Strength checks and Strength saving throws, and Advantage on Dexterity checks and Dexterity saving throws.<br /><br /><strong>Reduce Density</strong>. While the weight of a creature is doubled by this effect, the creature's Speed is reduced by 10 feet, it has Advantage on Strength checks and Strength saving throws, and Disadvantage on Dexterity checks and Dexterity saving throws.<br /><br />Upon reaching 10th level in this class, you can target an object or a creature that is Huge or smaller.</p>",
